yingyinNormal.en: But the dolphin did not invent the Sonar, it developed it naturally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但海豚并没有发明声纳，而是自然演化出声纳。

yingyinNormal.zh: 很显然我姐姐没跟你解释它是什么，从哪来。

yingyinNormal.en: A wormhole's not a naturally occurring phenomenon. Someone placed it there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虫洞不会自然形成。是有人放在那里的。

yingyinNormal.en: Naturally, we wondered if he'd tried to make contact. Not with me, Sergeant, no.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自然，我们想问问他有没有联络您。没联络我，警长，没有。

yingyinNormal.en: My bad. I just naturally assumed you came from some little carrot-choked Podunk. No?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的错，我只是觉得你肯定是从遍地胡萝卜的屯里来的吧？

yingyinNormal.en: One great structure that didn't rise naturally from the Earth, is China's Great Wall.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一依靠人工拔地而起的伟大建筑就是中国长城。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah. Well, I would, naturally. However, there is one little problem. You see them?
yingyinNormal.zh: 哈，是啊，我会的，当然会啦！但是这里有个小问题，看到他们没有？

yingyinNormal.en: Well naturally, the school has been searched many times. No such chamber has been found.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然学校人员进行过好几次的搜寻，但是并没有找到这样的密室。

yingyinNormal.en: And they have bones reinforced with naturally occurring carbon fiber. They are very hard to kill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的骨骼含有天生碳纤维，强壮坚硬极难杀死。

yingyinNormal.en: Watch a posture and physicality, this include everything from stand and naturally, to breathing from your diaphragm.

yingyinNormal.en: And when I thought about my challenge, balancing risk and reward, I realized that risk and reward naturally go together.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我考虑到自己的挑战，平衡风险和回报时，我意识到风险和回报是共存的。

yingyinNormal.en: Are people naturally good or evil? Good. All of you will argue good. Only one of you will argue the other side. Ms. Matthews.

yingyinNormal.en: By doing what comes naturally to us, we fail to account for our weaknesses and we crash. Either we keep doing that, or we change.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟从了我们的天性，就会忽视我们的弱点就会跌跤。要么继续下去，要么做出改变。

yingyinNormal.en: But no, because a doctor won't be able to help him, it's just gonna, you know, naturally pass through his system in like seven years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但医生也帮不了他，反正过个7年就会自动排出。

yingyinNormal.en: So, yeah, naturally, the guy with the name Fix-It Felix is the good guy. He's nice enough as good guys go. Definitely fixes stuff really well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，自然而然叫阿修的这个家伙才是好人，善良得跟所有君子一样。当然啦 他修理东西也一级棒。

examination_example.sentence: As robots take on ever more complex roles, the question <highlight>naturally</highlight> arises: Who will be responsible when they do something wrong?

examination_example.sentence: They breed <highlight>naturally</highlight> in corrosive ditches.

examination_example.sentence: Working-class parents, meanwhile, believe their children will <highlight>naturally</highlight> thrive, and give them far greater independence and time for free play.
